brewery.brewery_description:
We want you to enjoy fresh beer so we’ll be making it in small batches. We value community, so we’ll be collaborating with locals and drawing on local produce to create our range. We want everyone to find their “go to” beer and try something new, so we’ll have a core group of known favourites and some adventurous styles too. And, we will be preserving the craft of brewing.  

We look forward to having a beer with you.
